# Tiny-Todoist

A task management application built with React and Node.js/Express, **heavily inspired by the fantastic user experience of Todoist.**

This project was created for **educational purposes only** to practice full-stack development, modern web technologies, and UI/UX principles. It is not affiliated with, authorized, endorsed by, or in any way officially connected with Todoist or Doist Inc.

**All brand assets of Todoist (logos, icons, sounds) are the property of their respective owners.**
